            <div class="som-detes">
              <div class="background">
                <div class="about-profile">
                <%= cl_image_tag "present", height: 300, width: 220 %>
                <h3>About</h3>
                <p class="som-about">I'm a Pharmacist turned Fullstack Developer. I was born and raised in NW London (and also raised in Radlett, a village outside of London).</p>
                <p class="som-about">When I'm not coding, I'm either watching anime or dabbling in illustration and oil painting. If you like my site, don't hesitate to <a href="mailto:somakudu@gmail.com?subject=Hello!" target="_blank"><strong>reach out!</strong></a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-img">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-palette"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="about-profile">
                <%= cl_image_tag "soho", height: 300, width: 230 %>
                <h3>Communities</h3>
                <p class="som-about">Ever since completing my coding bootcamp, I have been an active member of <a href="https://www.lewagon.com/london" target="_blank"><strong>Le Wagon London</strong></a> where I teach other people part-time how to code. It is an incredible and diverse community that has been a rewarding part of my coding journey.</p>
                <p class="som-about" >I am also currently taking part of the <a href="https://www.blackgirlsintech.org/mentoring-programme" target="_blank"><strong>Black Girls in Tech</strong></a> Mentorship Programme where I meet other black women in tech to talk all things tech. <a href="https://codebar.io/" target="_blank"><strong>Code Bar</strong></a> is another community who's programming workshops I attend.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="pictures">
                <div class="about-profile">
                <div class="icon-img">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-laptop"></i>
                </div>
